<h2 id="changes" class="no-num">Change Log</h2>

<h3 id="changes-2026-05">USML 2026.05 — Editor's Draft</h3>

- Initial Editor's Draft.
- Defines: Conformance, Core Data Model, Aesthetic-Pack Interface, Backend
    Emission Contract, Ingest Interface, AI Consumption Format, Security
    Considerations, Privacy Considerations, Accessibility Considerations,
    Internationalization Considerations, Versioning and Stability,
    Conformance Test Suite (scaffold), Reference Implementation Conformance
    Claim, Terminology, Adoption Thresholds.
- Established USML/Quoin bifurcation: USML is the specification; Quoin is
    the reference implementation.

